    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>下载量突破2亿！全球玩家最爱的人气社交游戏！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可以与《天天玩乐园》手机版绑定，在Steam上轻松玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来《天天玩乐园》，认识来自世界各地的新朋友吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要内容</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由装扮专属角色，并与来自全球的玩家一起同乐。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来打造独一无二的专属角色吧！ 多种肤色、发型、体型、服饰，任你挑选！ 还能遇见来自世界各地各种新朋友，一起聊天、互动，说不定还能擦出火花，成为情侣呢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e45db5160b77c68dafc6ef0e0878b3e0.poster.avif?t=1772065686\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e45db5160b77c68dafc6ef0e0878b3e0.webm?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e45db5160b77c68dafc6ef0e0878b3e0.mp4?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造梦想家园，并邀请好友参加家庭派对吧！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过多种风格的房屋和家具，让梦想中的家园化为现实。 邀请好友或造访好友家，一起钓鱼、玩游戏、聊天等，度过愉快的时光吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/90b6d3a6ba3b1fc27e2ba6197f183ce3.poster.avif?t=1772065686\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/90b6d3a6ba3b1fc27e2ba6197f183ce3.webm?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/90b6d3a6ba3b1fc27e2ba6197f183ce3.mp4?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与好友挑战各种有趣的小游戏吧！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与30人竞争，成为最后的赢家，尽情享受「大家一起游戏派对」「僵尸病毒」「障碍物奔跑」「无限之塔」「时尚达人」「SnowWars.io」「登上高空」和学校小游戏等，展现你的实力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e992d292f5a8a48ab2b498eb6718b9ad.poster.avif?t=1772065686\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e992d292f5a8a48ab2b498eb6718b9ad.webm?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198850/extras/e992d292f5a8a48ab2b498eb6718b9ad.mp4?t=1772065686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在不同的钓鱼场地捕捉新奇鱼类，展现钓鱼成就吧！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在池塘、海洋、泳池等各种地方钓鱼，种类甚至超达600种。 鱼种将不断更新，让你时刻充满新鲜感。 每个钓鱼场地还有特殊鱼种，快来完成图鉴，并和好友炫耀吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>和好友在各处捕捉昆虫和蜥蜴，挖掘稀有的矿物和化石吧！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过300种的昆虫等你捕捉！ 还能体验挖掘恐龙化石和稀有钻石的趣味。 获得后可以贩售，也可以当作展示品，让好友们欣赏一下你的收藏吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用心养育各种宠物吧！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以让小狗、猫咪、小马等各种宠物跟随在自己身边，为你的《天天玩乐园》生活带来不同的乐趣。 和朋友一起遛宠物、开着梦想跑车兜风吧！ 甚至还有期间限定的宠物，快来看看！</p>",
